'''Uga Shrine''' (宇賀神社, うがじんじゃ) is a Shinto shrine dedicated to {{ill|Ukanomitama|ja|ウカノミタマ|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (宇迦之御魂神, 倉稲魂命) or {{ill|Ugajin|ja|宇賀神|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.
* A shrine located in Yamamoto, Yamakizaki, {{ill|Imabetsu Town|ja|今別町|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Aomori Prefecture|ja|青森県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * A shrine in Miyamoto Kō, {{ill|Tajima|ja|田島|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Minamiaizu Town|ja|南会津町|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Fukushima Prefecture|ja|福島県|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - {{ill|Tade Uga Shrine|ja|田出宇賀神社|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * A shrine in {{ill|Fuma|ja|府馬|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Katori City|ja|香取市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Chiba Prefecture|ja|千葉県|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - Known for the {{ill|Great Camphor Tree of Fuma|ja|府馬の大クス|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * A shrine in Iizasa, {{ill|Tako Town|ja|多古町|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, Chiba Prefecture - {{ill|Uga Shrine (Tako Town, Iizasa)|ja|宇賀神社 (多古町飯笹)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * A shrine in Nishikoiso, {{ill|Ōiso Town|ja|大磯町|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Kanagawa Prefecture|ja|神奈川県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * A shrine on Biwa Island in {{ill|Lake Nojiri|ja|野尻湖|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Shinanomachi|ja|信濃町|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Nagano Prefecture|ja|長野県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * A shrine in Chirihama Town, {{ill|Hakui City|ja|羽咋市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Ishikawa Prefecture|ja|石川県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * A shrine in Higashi Satsuzucho, Higashikujo, {{ill|Minami Ward, Kyoto|ja|南区|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Kyoto City|ja|京都市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Kyoto Prefecture|ja|京都府|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * A shrine in Kasada Kasaoka, {{ill|Toyonaka Town (Mitoyo)|ja|豊中町|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Mitoyo City|ja|三豊市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Kagawa Prefecture|ja|香川県|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - Known for the Doburoku Festival. * A shrine in Sukumo Valley, {{ill|Kitanada Town|ja|北灘町|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Naruto City|ja|鳴門市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Tokushima Prefecture|ja|徳島県|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - {{ill|Iuga Shrine|ja|伊宇賀神社|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * A shrine in Nyūgawa, {{ill|Saijō City|ja|西条市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Ehime Prefecture|ja|愛媛県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * A shrine in Nagahama, {{ill|Kōchi City|ja|高知市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Kōchi Prefecture|ja|高知県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * A shrine in Ōmiya, {{ill|Chūō Ward, Fukuoka|ja|大宮 (福岡市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Fukuoka City|ja|福岡市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Fukuoka Prefecture|ja|福岡県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * A shrine in Ikino Matsubara, {{ill|Nishi Ward, Fukuoka|ja|生の松原 (福岡市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, Fukuoka City - Shimoyamato Uga Shrine. * A shrine in Kodabe, {{ill|Sawara Ward, Fukuoka|ja|小田部|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, Fukuoka City - Shōgun Shrine. * A shrine in Koinumaru, {{ill|Yoshitomi Town|ja|吉富町|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, Fukuoka Prefecture - Uga Kibune Shrine.
