* A shrine located in Yamamoto, Yamakizaki, [[:en:Imabetsu|Imabetsu Town]], [[:en:Aomori Prefecture|Aomori Prefecture]]. * A shrine in Miyamoto Kō, {{ill|Tajima|ja|田島|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tajima|qq=}}, [[:en:Minamiaizu|Minamiaizu Town]], [[:en:Fukushima Prefecture|Fukushima Prefecture]] - {{ill|Tade Uga Shrine|ja|田出宇賀神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tade Uga Shrine|qq=}}. * A shrine in {{ill|Fuma|ja|府馬|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fuma|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, [[:en:Katori, Chiba|Katori City]], [[:en:Chiba Prefecture|Chiba Prefecture]] - Known for the {{ill|Great Camphor Tree of Fuma|ja|府馬の大クス|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Great Camphor Tree of Fuma|qq=}}. * A shrine in Iizasa, [[:en:Tako, Chiba|Tako Town]], Chiba Prefecture - {{ill|Uga Shrine (Tako Town, Iizasa)|ja|宇賀神社 (多古町飯笹)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Uga Shrine (Tako Town, Iizasa)|qq=}}. * A shrine in Nishikoiso, [[:en:Ōiso|Ōiso Town]], [[:en:Kanagawa Prefecture|Kanagawa Prefecture]]. * A shrine on Biwa Island in [[:en:Lake Nojiri|Lake Nojiri]], [[:en:Shinano, Nagano|Shinanomachi]], [[:en:Nagano Prefecture|Nagano Prefecture]]. * A shrine in Chirihama Town, [[:en:Hakui, Ishikawa|Hakui City]], [[:en:Ishikawa Prefecture|Ishikawa Prefecture]]. * A shrine in Higashi Satsuzucho, Higashikujo, {{ill|Minami Ward, Kyoto|ja|南区|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minami Ward, Kyoto|qq=}}, [[:en:Kyoto|Kyoto City]], [[:en:Kyoto Prefecture|Kyoto Prefecture]]. * A shrine in Kasada Kasaoka, {{ill|Toyonaka Town (Mitoyo)|ja|豊中町|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Toyonaka Town (Mitoyo)|qq=}}, [[:en:Mitoyo, Kagawa|Mitoyo City]], [[:en:Kagawa Prefecture|Kagawa Prefecture]] - Known for the Doburoku Festival. * A shrine in Sukumo Valley, {{ill|Kitanada Town|ja|北灘町|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kitanada Town|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 北灘村 (徳島県)}}, [[:en:Naruto, Tokushima|Naruto City]], [[:en:Tokushima Prefecture|Tokushima Prefecture]] - {{ill|Iuga Shrine|ja|伊宇賀神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Iuga Shrine|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}. * A shrine in Nyūgawa, [[:en:Saijō, Ehime|Saijō City]], [[:en:Ehime Prefecture|Ehime Prefecture]]. * A shrine in Nagahama, [[:en:Kōchi, Kōchi|Kōchi City]], [[:en:Kōchi Prefecture|Kōchi Prefecture]]. * A shrine in Ōmiya, {{ill|Chūō Ward, Fukuoka|ja|大宮 (福岡市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chūō Ward, Fukuoka|qq=}}, [[:en:Fukuoka|Fukuoka City]], [[:en:Fukuoka Prefecture|Fukuoka Prefecture]]. * A shrine in Ikino Matsubara, {{ill|Nishi Ward, Fukuoka|ja|生の松原 (福岡市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nishi Ward, Fukuoka|qq=}}, Fukuoka City - Shimoyamato Uga Shrine. * A shrine in Kodabe, {{ill|Sawara Ward, Fukuoka|ja|小田部|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sawara Ward, Fukuoka|qq=}}, Fukuoka City - Shōgun Shrine. * A shrine in Koinumaru, [[:en:Yoshitomi, Fukuoka|Yoshitomi Town]], Fukuoka Prefecture - Uga Kibune Shrine.
